<lb ed="GA" n="0015a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">凡例</cb:mulu><head>鄧尉聖恩寺志凡例</head>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a02"/><list style="margin-left:1em;"><item xml:id="itemGA042p0015a0201"><note n="0015a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0015a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>山占地勝，寺占山勝，非繪圖幅，不能總攬形
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a03"/>勢，故鐫圖置之卷首。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a04"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0015a0401"><note n="0015a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0015a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>舊志有本志，今因之，但欲<reg>刊</reg>定山名，不嫌<g ref="#CB18591"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a05"/>考，故特遍加叅詳，為卷之一。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a06"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0015a0601"><note n="0015a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0015a0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>舊志有泉石，今亦因之，此今昔無改也，為卷
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a07"/>之二。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0015a08"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0015a0801"><note n="0015a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0015a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>舊志有梵宇、有山居，今總為梵宇，而以山寺、
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA042.0042.0016a" n="0016a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a01"/>山菴、山居並列，以其皆屬淨地也，為卷之三。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a02"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0016a0201"><note n="0016a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0016a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>舊志有名釋，今欲推重燈傳，故分禪祖為卷
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a03"/>之四，名釋為卷之五。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a04"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0016a0401"><note n="0016a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0016a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>舊志止於集詩集文，故以　賜詩　敕諭冠
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a05"/>兩者之首。今詩文裒聚<reg>既</reg>多，臚分各異，故特
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a06"/>尊　聖製，不與他作同卷，為卷之六。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a07"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0016a0701"><note n="0016a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0016a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>昔併菴為寺，寺以初創，今改書院為禪院，寺
<lb ed="GA" n="0016a08"/>以中興，又寺額　賜出　天朝，稽諸案牘，皆
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA042.0042.0017a" n="0017a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a01"/>有考據，故以奏疏公移為卷之七。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a02"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0017a0201"><note n="0017a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0017a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>有寺則有記，記所以永寺也，故以寺記為卷
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a03"/>之八。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a04"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0017a0401"><note n="0017a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0017a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>有禪祖則有語錄，錄所以行禪也，故以語錄
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a05"/>為卷之九。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a06"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0017a0601"><note n="0017a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0017a0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>有錄則有序，序所以弁錄也，故以錄序為卷
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a07"/>之十。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0017a08"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0017a0801"><note n="0017a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0017a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>寺之興，與寺之復、僧之聚，無不取資檀施，故
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA042.0042.0018a" n="0018a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a01"/>以募疏為卷之十一。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a02"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0018a0201"><note n="0018a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0018a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>禪語所繇成錄，本於勸請說法，故以請疏為
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a03"/>卷之十二。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a04"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0018a0401"><note n="0018a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0018a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>舊志有祠墓介于泉石梵宇之間，今志歸重
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a05"/>禪寺，故以塔廟為卷之十三，而祠墓附載不
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a06"/>盡，則有郡邑兩志在也。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a07"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0018a0701"><note n="0018a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0018a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>有塔則有銘，銘所以表塔也，故以塔銘為卷
<lb ed="GA" n="0018a08"/>之十四。</item>
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA042.0042.0019a" n="0019a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a01"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0019a0101"><note n="0019a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0019a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>鐘為寺鎮，法華鐘更為法寶，其因緣功德甚
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a02"/>大，非他器可比，故特列鐘部為卷之十五。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a03"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0019a0301"><note n="0019a0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0019a0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>名山名刹，時有名人來游，而不盡作記，記所
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a04"/>以表山刹也，故以遊記為卷之十六。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a05"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0019a0501"><note n="0019a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0019a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>名人之作，記少詩多，詩所繇作亦多種，總不
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a06"/>離山刹，故以題詠為卷之十七。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a07"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0019a0701"><note n="0019a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0019a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>名文有為此山作，而非前諸條所得類收者，
<lb ed="GA" n="0019a08"/>當別載以附見，故以雜文為卷之十八。其詩
<pb ed="GA" xml:id="GA042.0042.0020a" n="0020a"/>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a01"/>文之外，偶拾片語，亦資多識，故以雜記終焉。</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a02"/><item xml:id="itemGA042p0020a0201"><note n="0020a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="0020a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>凡書例有目錄在前，今<reg>既</reg>已條次其說，遂不
<lb ed="GA" n="0020a03"/>更復出。</item></list></cb:div>
